\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>6. Grand Bassin, Mauritius<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Grand Bassin is an inactive volcano crater lake. A priest from India once brought sacred water and poured holy water into the lake. It now is a sacred place for a large number of Hindu people in Mauritius.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/maurtius-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find all places to stay on Mauritius<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23160954\/things-to-do-mauritius-grand-bassin-buddha-640x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"267\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"5605\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23160954\/things-to-do-mauritius-grand-bassin-buddha.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/destinations\/things-to-do-mauritius\/attachment\/things-to-do-mauritius-grand-bassin-buddha\/\" class=\"wp-image-5605 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23160954\/things-to-do-mauritius-grand-bassin-buddha-64