<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to get around Mauritius<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mauritius is relatively small and getting around by Taxi or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-mauritius\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">rental car<\/a> is the best option. Roads on the island are very well connected and apps like Google Maps also work. Getting from the airport to another side of this island takes you 1 to 1.5 hours. <strong>Good to know:<\/strong> In Mauritius driving is on the left-hand side.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you&#x2019;re planning on renting a car on Mauritius we recommend&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-mauritius\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. When booking through them, all insurances are included. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-mauritius\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"budget\">Costs of traveling on Mauritius<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mauritius can be done on a budget, a double room in a budget hotel would cost you between &#x20AC;40 and &#x20AC;75 but a luxury stay can easily be &#x20AC;200 or more a night.<br><br>Street food or self-catering will start at &#x20AC;5 per lunch and amazing food in a top-end restaurant will start at &#x20AC;50 per lunch.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple.jpg\" alt=\"beach mauritius\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"beach mauritius\" class=\"wp-image-5523 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/23161105\/Beautiful-resort-mauritius-beach-couple-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\